    public abstract class EdgeTripletRDD<ED,​VD>
extends org.apache.spark.rdd.RDD<EdgeTriplet<ED,​VD>>
    An RDD that stores a collection of edge triplets with interface for the data type as `EdgeTriplet`. The data should be essentially stored as a collection of `EdgeTripletPartition` instances.
